@startuml
title PartnerProfile Lifecycle - 3.6 (PartnerStatus)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #EEECFB
  BorderColor #8B7FD6
  FontColor #1A1A1A
  ArrowColor #444444
}
hide empty description

[*] --> PENDING : Customer submits KYC\n(POST /api/partners/register)
PENDING --> APPROVED : Admin approves\n(grant PARTNER role)
PENDING --> REJECTED : Admin rejects (+ reason)
REJECTED --> PENDING : Partner resubmits KYC
APPROVED --> SUSPENDED : Admin suspends
SUSPENDED --> APPROVED : Admin restores

APPROVED : Partner workspace unlocked
SUSPENDED : Operational sanction\n(admin-only to lift)
@enduml
